From: (USANYS) 
Sent: Friday, September 13, 2019 2:22 PM 
To: (USANYS) < 
Subject: Re: Epstein -- Release of USMS information 
Can you forward to me the more problematic articles. 
On Sep 13, 2019, at 2:01 PM, (USANYS)<> wrote: 
As you are undoubtedly aware, there has been some press coverage since yesterday about the release pursuant to POIA 
of some USMS records. I just spoke with the Associate General Counsel at the USMS, who wanted to provide us with 
the actual source materials (USM 11s (equivalent of 302s)) that were inadvertently released, because they were not in 
all circumstances accurately reported, and he wanted to make sure that if we are concerned about any harm to our 
investigation from the release, that we have the original materials. He also offered to serve as a POC if we have any 
questions. 
Chief, Criminal Division 
United States Attorney's Office, SDNY 
EFTA00024171
